## Compatibility {#compatibility}

Goldfish cohabitation is limited by their temperature requirements (cool water) and their tendency to eat smaller fish.

**Compatible with goldfish:**
- Other goldfish of similar size (avoid mixing fast single-tail with slow fancy varieties)
- [Bristlenose Plecos](/species/bristlenose-pleco) — tolerate cooler water; useful algae cleaners in goldfish tanks
- White Cloud Mountain Minnows — cold-tolerant schooling fish too fast for goldfish to catch
- Weather/Dojo Loach — cold-tolerant benthic fish

**Incompatible:**
- Tropical fish (temperature incompatibility)
- Small fish that fit in goldfish mouths
- Aggressive fin-nippers

